PortGroup           golang 1.0

go.setup            github.com/lima-vm/lima 0.19.0 v
go.offline_build    no
github.tarball_from archive
revision            0

homepage            https://lima-vm.io

description         Linux virtual machines

long_description    {*}${description}

categories          sysutils
installs_libs       no
license             Apache-2
